{"tid":1212344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真系列】香港人今日敗了一仗 但我地不但無輸到 仲睇到希望","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:55:43.000Z","uid":59305,"like":94,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb46d413cc3c10c0a32b26c8a49fd5e45e061154","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:20.000Z","msg":"今日瞓晏覺時發咗個夢 想分享下<br />\n<br />\n標題嘅呢一句 係我今日對所見所聞嘅一句總結 由今朝喺夏愨道同添美道交界物資站叫咪同大家交流 到班狗放催淚彈打到尾時 我只想同大家講一句:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 真係好叻 好勇敢 多謝你地 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日見到嘅大家 喺冇分化 無篤灰 無割席 大家都好願意去溝通 完全一條心 <br />\n無論係需要物資時嘅一呼百應 抑或是對小弟長達幾分鐘大叫&quot;撒回&quot;嘅咆哮配合 無一不令我感受到香港人嘅團結 <br />\n<br />\n對於慣咗和理非嘅香港人 當頭幾粒催淚彈啱啱飛出嚟嘅時候 <br />\n明顯係顯得有啲驚惶失措 甚至可以用雞飛狗走嚟形容 當然亦都係人之常情 <br />\n<br />\n但驚慌過後不久 各單位好快就進入狀態 前線勇士不斷勇猛抵擋盾牌狗嘅攻勢 而後勤小隊喺勇士暫時退後時爭取時間為佢哋療傷 而有大聲公嘅就嘗試去指揮進退嘅節奏 同埋不斷提醒後方嘅人支援嘅重要性 而於後方觀望嘅一大群喜出望外地開始勇敢起嚟 識上前補位 同埋進退時會照顧身邊嘅戰友 <br />\n<br />\n我眼見呢一幕時真係覺得非常感動 就係因為大家良好嘅配合 我地不致於被一擊即潰 即使處於劣勢 仍然可以有條理地慢慢向後退 <br />\n<br />\n當物資站失守後 盾牌狗攻出夏愨道並繼續使用催淚彈向中環方向推進 喺過程中群眾開始潰退 有唔少人向海富中心退咗就無再返嚟 <br />\n<br />\n正當我心諗場仗係咪要就咁輸時 附近前線嘅勇士 開始識用頭盔 濕毛巾等等招數去對付催淚彈 潰敗中嘅防線奇跡地開始喺海富中心橋底停咗 <br />\n<br />\n有見呢個情況 我即刻拎埋個咪衝去二線分享前線所用嘅方法 而當佢地學識咗後即刻上前支援 <br />\n我好記得有一波催淚彈的攻勢大概有十粒到 但前線二線嘅勇士好快速就解決哂呢波催淚彈 並開始建立起新一層嘅防線<br />\n<br />\n喺呢刻其實後排嘅人 已經退到去遠東金融中心位置 前線二線同埋後排之間只有極零散嘅人喺入面 個斷層其實非常危險 但當我每一次去後排做教學時 大家都會好全神貫注咁聽 聽完後就連人帶物資衝番上海富橋底嘅防線 最後竟然重新塞爆夏愨道後半段 <br />\n<br />\n前方嘅戰線不但可以抵擋住催淚彈嘅攻勢 而且仲有餘力去打走喺橋上邊想攻落嚟嘅盾牌狗 大家嘅眼中都散發出希望嘅光芒 呢一次亦係我第一次覺得香港人真係有可能會成功 喺海富橋底 我記憶中好似守咗差唔多25至30分鐘有多 諗番起都覺得大家好犀利<br />\n<br />\n最後雖然我地無鐵馬而被盾牌狗用衝擊攻勢而瓦解咗 但係先天條件極不利嘅情況之下 (沒有訓練 裝備落差 通訊不良 久未抗爭) 即使敗 都敗得漂亮 更何況 今日都令到二讀無法開會 雖然血的代價 真係非常沉重&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n今日嘅仗 雖然先敗首陣 <br />\n但我地因為今次嘅經驗而大大咁成長咗 <br />\n下一場嘅抗惡法戰爭<br />\n希望你地會相信自己 相信今日喺金鐘現在同你並肩作戰嘅香港人<br />\n再次一齊企出嚟打呢場硬仗<br />\n我都會繼續略盡綿力 與大家同行<br />\n因為你地 我相信香港人今次會贏<br />\n所以 香港加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b35dacc7823cb148cbac131e1d6e98e9b8b965e","tid":1212344,"uid":209543,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ae87496e351d97d0ad0a6d223ddb131e8bd6b30","tid":1212344,"uid":249376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"香港人真心好勁好醒目<br />\n6月9比人撚完<br />\n6月12就可以做到55波<br />\n之後會唔會有機會撚返啲狗轉頭呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩撚大左啦 連美帝都出聲</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1dc20a369f5af2f2b7a276b3f6b4e733a8881dd","tid":1212344,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"嚇到唔敢開會已經好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276d829b0f81043feb44c6acef25f99c7812bc85","tid":1212344,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"大家有共識行動，請幫手推<br />\n<br />\n613行動部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69de234af11c2d8a2f691fb2c6131f4728defed2","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ae87496e351d97d0ad0a6d223ddb131e8bd6b30","tid":1212344,"uid":249376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"香港人真心好勁好醒目<br />\n6月9比人撚完<br />\n6月12就可以做到55波<br />\n之後會唔會有機會撚返啲狗轉頭呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩撚大左啦 連美帝都出聲</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:49:15.000Z","msg":"今日海富橋底失守係因為我地無鐵馬 事關班狗射勁撚多催淚彈都無用 佢地轉用衝打 所以就守唔到 但下次唔會了 大家會識守"},{"pid":"ca95e9314ef742ddd6132e2b1f0a39212b39102f","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa3f94974113df81315dc61317b9ac838db06c72","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:07:42.000Z","msg":"希望大家都會睇到希望 會繼續行出嚟"},{"pid":"3a889fb4826220d780db072845cb9194f961858e","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"keep pushing."},{"pid":"8e55bac18bcbc54242f38aeef0055d41ae9b1b37","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"希望推到所有香港人都睇到希望"},{"pid":"b7a50cb512e257cf72884bd82aeb1725c60cbe16","tid":1212344,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"至少拖到兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6e9314dff8f04d7ba44e1ddd172b5e0898838b","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a50cb512e257cf72884bd82aeb1725c60cbe16","tid":1212344,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"至少拖到兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"香港今次真係有機會 所以要加油"},{"pid":"f4790b1d8b3d9d5f5a2da4e7e1979698655cf37b","tid":1212344,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6e9314dff8f04d7ba44e1ddd172b5e0898838b","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a50cb512e257cf72884bd82aeb1725c60cbe16","tid":1212344,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"至少拖到兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"香港今次真係有機會 所以要加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc075b86f34a0c7b8333e31dd08c5a638a993a7","tid":1212344,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"香港人好勁！<br />\n<br />\n警犬full gear之下，都差不多可以5-5波！"},{"pid":"2b7c18cad30240df2d1075edbc669c9de4620d0b","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bc075b86f34a0c7b8333e31dd08c5a638a993a7","tid":1212344,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"香港人好勁！<br />\n<br />\n警犬full gear之下，都差不多可以5-5波！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"所以香港人經過咗今次經驗 絕對有機會贏 只要大家唔放棄 下一次同樣會出嚟 就得"},{"pid":"78dad148e2a8ad6ddba960dd092086283dfbae36","tid":1212344,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"push"}]}